<h2 style="font-size:40px;">ğŸ’» Project Overview</h2>
<p>
<strong>Apni Dukan</strong> allows users to:
</p>
<ul>
  <li>Browse and search for products</li>
  <li>Register and log in as a user</li>
  <li>Add products to cart and manage orders</li>
  <li>Experience a responsive and user-friendly UI</li>
</ul>

<h2 style="font-size:40px;">ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Frontend: React.js, Tailwind CSS</li>
  <li>Backend: Node.js, Express.js</li>
  <li>Database: MongoDB</li>
  <li>Authentication: JWT, Bcrypt</li>
</ul>

<h2 style="font-size:40px;">ğŸš€ Features</h2>
<ul>
  <li>User authentication and authorization</li>
  <li>Product listing, filtering, and search</li>
  <li>Shopping cart and order management</li>
  <li>Responsive design for mobile and desktop</li>
</ul>

<h2 style="font-size:40px;">ğŸ“‚ How to Run</h2>
<ol>
  <li>Clone the repo: <code>git clone https://github.com/MOHITGODARA1/ApniDukan.git</code></li>
  <li>Install dependencies: <code>npm install</code></li>
  <li>Start the server: <code>npm run dev</code></li>
  <li>Open <code>http://localhost:5173</code> in your browser</li>
</ol>

